# Project Context

This is the one file that tells you how this project is built and how to work in it. Read the canonical files below and derive the stack and commands from them — do not guess scripts, versions, or dependencies. Update the `@`-paths and the TODOs to match this repository.

> The `@`-paths below (`@package.json`, `@tsconfig.json`, etc.) are placeholders. They resolve once this kit is installed into a real project; fill or remove them to match the repo.

